# Smartup24 — Loyiha Bilim Bazasi

## Proyekt haqida
- Playwright + Python (pytest) UI test avtomatizatsiyasi — Smartup24 (x24) ERP tizimi
- Framework: pytest + playwright-python (+ allure-pytest report uchun)
- URL: https://app3.greenwhite.uz/x24/a2/auth/login
- Default login: admin@autotest / greenwhite (flows/flow_authorization.py da)
- UI: yangi Angular `smt-*` komponentlari (eski `b-input`/`biruni` EMAS)

## Katalog tuzilmasi (tekis / flat)
```
conftest.py            — pytest fixtures + allure setup + failure screenshot
utils/base_page.py     — BasePage: barcha forma amallari uchun universal funksiyalar
flows/
  flow_authorization.py  — authorization(page, email, password), logout(page)
  flow_navbar.py         — flow_navigate(page, tab, name), flow_search(), flow_menu()
tests/
  test_manufacturer.py   — run_manufacturer / test_manufacturer  (eng sodda namuna)
  test_industry.py       — run_industry / test_industry
  test_category.py       — run_category / test_category
  test_product.py        — run_product / test_product
  test_all.py            — test_all: barcha run_* ni bitta login bilan zanjir qiladi
skills/skills/*/SKILL.md — write-test, debug-test, run-smoke, new-flow, review-test, learn
pytest.ini             — testpaths=., python_files=test_*.py
```
Eski `tests/smoke/`, group runnerlar, `scripts/run_tests.py`, `.env`, company/telegram mexanizmi YO'Q.

## conftest.py — Fixtures

| Fixture | Scope | Tavsif |
|---------|-------|--------|
| `browser` | function | Yangi Chromium (headless=False, --start-maximized) |
| `page` | function | Yangi context+page + trace + teardownda `logout()` |
| `session_browser`/`session_context`/`session_page` | session | Chain uchun yagona browser/context/page |
| `code` | session | random 4-xonali son (str) — unikal nom uchun |
| `save_data` / `load_data` | session | `test-results/data/data_store.json` ga yozish/o'qish |

Timeout: `DEFAULT_TIMEOUT=10_000` ms, `NAVIGATION_TIMEOUT=60_000` ms.

## BasePage (utils/base_page.py) — asosiy metodlar
Element `label` (ko'rinadigan matn) yoki barqaror `smtid` orqali topiladi.

```python
m = BasePage(page)
m.input(label="Название", value="...")            # smt-input (label yoki smtid=)
m.select("кг", label="measure")                    # smt-data-select (Подбор)
m.multiselect("A", "B", label="Роли")              # multi select
m.radio("Активный", label="Статус")                # smt-radio-group (value A/P/S)
m.checkbox(label="Статус", checked=True)           # smt-switch YOKI smt-checkbox (toggle)
m.grid_row(name, "Активный")                       # .smt-data-row (matn + contains)
m.click_grid_row("Отрасль")                        # qatorni bosish (+ _settle)
m.search("matn")                                    # searchbox "Поиск..."
m.click_link("Производители")                       # sub-nav bo'lim link (+ _settle)
m.open_create()                                     # "Создать" (+ _settle)
m.click_button("Подтипы")                          # ixtiyoriy tugma
m.save_and_expect_heading("Товары")                 # "Сохранить" + heading
m.expect_heading("...") / m.current_heading_text() # aktiv title span
m.wait_for_loader()                                 # app-global-page-loader
```

## UI patternlar (Smartup24 x24)
- Text input: `smt-input[smtid]` → ichki `input`; label `div.flex.flex-col > label`.
- Select: `smt-data-select[smtid]` → `input[placeholder="Подбор"]`; dropdown `.cdk-overlay-container smt-select-dropdown li`. Tanlangach qiymat select MATNIDA emas, Подбор INPUT value'sida.
- Radio (Статус): `smt-radio-group[smtid]` → `label[smt-radio]` (value A/P/S).
- Grid qatori: `.smt-data-row`.
- Radio vs Switch: Статус ba'zi formalarda `smt-radio-group` (radio), ba'zilarida `smt-switch` (gorizontal, `<span>` label) — `radio(...)` yoki `checkbox(...)`. Toggle ichida `input[type=checkbox]` (holat) + `[role=switch]` (bosiladi).
- Heading: `app-form-stack-widget span.font-semibold.truncate` (FAQAT title). Widgetning butun matni sub-nav LINK nomlarini ham oladi — `to_contain_text` butun widgetda premature match beradi, shuning uchun `expect_heading` faqat title span ni tekshiradi.
- Ikki router-outlet: sub-header (title) va asosiy kontent (`smartup24-app-*-list`, "Создать" shu yerda) asinxron yangilanadi. Faqat heading kutish yetmaydi — `click_link`/`open_create`/`click_grid_row` ichidagi `_settle()` (loader+networkidle) kontent almashguncha kutadi. Sub-nav'ga `click_link(name)` bilan o't.
- Login tekshiruvi universal: `authorization` "Модератор" tugmasini emas, URL (login'dan chiqish) + `app-user-dropdown` (har login sahifada bor) ni kutadi.
- **Dinamik `input[name="ng.formN.*"]` va `#cdk-drop-list-N` ISHLATMA** — har run'da o'zgaradi.

## Test konvensiyasi (run_ + test_)
- `run_<nomi>(page, code)` — biznes logika, login qilinganini kutadi; `test_all` chaqiradi.
- `test_<nomi>(page, code)` — `authorization(page)` + `run_<nomi>(...)` (alohida run uchun).
- Unikal nom `f"...{code}"`; har navigatsiya/save dan keyin `expect_heading(...)`.
- Barcha forma amallari `BasePage` orqali; navbar/link/tugma uchun raw `get_by_role`.
- Yangi test `tests/test_all.py` zanjiriga qo'shiladi.

## Ishga tushirish
```bash
.venv/bin/python -m pytest tests/test_all.py -v          # to'liq zanjir
.venv/bin/python -m pytest tests/test_product.py -v      # bitta fayl
allure serve test-results/allure-results                 # report
```
Yangi UI patternni yozishdan oldin Playwright MCP bilan real DOM'da tasdiqla — fieldlarni taxmin qilma.
